<subSubSection pageId="96" pageNumber="97" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="96.[151,1437,942,1401]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">
REMARKS: 
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[267,501,1230,1257]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" refId="ref368401" refString="Rondani, C. (1857) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: II. Species italicae ordinis dipterorum in genera characteribus definita, ordinatim collectae, methodo analitica distinctae, et novis vel minus cognitis descriptis. Pars prima. Oestridae: Syrphfidae [sic!]: Conopidae. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 264 pp., 1 pl. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1857">Rondani (1857: 225)</bibRefCitation>
described 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1857" box="[623,913,1231,1257]" genus="Sphixosoma" kingdom="Animalia" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" rank="species" species="aureifasciata">
<emphasis box="[623,913,1231,1257]" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Sphixosoma aureifasciata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from just the male sex, without specifying the exact 
<taxonomicName box="[267,353,1267,1293]" family="Number" pageId="96" pageNumber="26" rank="family">number</taxonomicName>
of specimens, but giving a single measurement of length: “ 
<emphasis box="[1033,1384,1267,1293]" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">
Mas speciei semel a me 
<taxonomicName box="[1311,1384,1267,1292]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Semel" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="captus">captus</taxonomicName>
</emphasis>
[the male of this species collected by me once]”. 
<bibRefCitation author="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Mei, M." box="[712,1063,1303,1329]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" pagination="271 - 277" refId="ref365784" refString="Rivosecchi, L. &amp; Mei, M. (1998) Note sinonimiche su alcuni Conopidi descritti da Camillo Rondani (Diptera Conopidae). Fragmenta Entomologica, 30 (2), 271 - 277." type="journal article" year="1998">Rivosecchi &amp; Mei (1998: 272)</bibRefCitation>
designated a 
<typeStatus box="[1220,1323,1303,1329]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">lectotype</typeStatus>
(
<specimenCount box="[1341,1364,1303,1329]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" type="male">♂</specimenCount>
). This nominal species was described under the generic name 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1857" box="[846,967,1339,1365]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Spixosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[846,967,1339,1365]" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Spixosoma</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, which is an “unjustified emendation of 
<taxonomicName authority="Rondani, 1856" authorityName="Rondani" authorityYear="1856" box="[199,513,1374,1401]" class="Insecta" family="Conopidae" genus="Sphyxosoma" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Diptera" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis box="[199,339,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">Sphyxosoma</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Rondani, C." box="[346,513,1374,1401]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" refId="ref368338" refString="Rondani, C. (1856) Dipterologiae italicae prodromus. Vol: I. Genera italica ordinis dipterorum ordinatim disposita et distincta et in familias et stirpes aggregata. A. Stocchi, Parmae [= Parma], 226 pp. + [2] pp. https: // doi. org / 10.5962 / bhl. title. 8160" type="book" year="1856">Rondani, 1856</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
” (
<bibRefCitation author="O'Hara, J. E. &amp; Cerretti, P. &amp; Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L." box="[538,809,1375,1401]" pageId="96" pageNumber="97" pagination="1 - 268" refId="ref361577" refString="O'Hara, J. E., Cerretti, P., Pape, T. &amp; Evenhuis, N. L. (2011) Nomenclatural studies toward a world list of Diptera genus-group names. Part II: Camillo Rondani. Zootaxa, 3141, 1 - 268. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3141.1.1" type="journal article" year="2011">
O’Hara 
<emphasis box="[631,687,1375,1401]" italics="true" pageId="96" pageNumber="97">et al.</emphasis>
2011: 170
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
